## Detailed Terms

### Section 1: Definitions

1.1 **"Morget Software"** means the source code, compiled binaries, scripts, APIs, libraries, and any associated backend or frontend code originally released under this license by Moonlight Games (MG), MGFeng, or Feng.

1.2 **"Morget Assets"** means any non-code resources distributed alongside Morget Software, including:
- (a) **"Documentation"** — user guides, API references, tutorials, and explanatory text;
- (b) **"Media"** — images, fonts, icons, and other visual elements (excluding the official Logo and Brand Identity);
- (c) **"Brand Assets"** — the official logos, mascots, color schemes, and visual identity elements of Moonlight Games (MG). Detailed usage rules are defined in separate TRADEMARK.md and BRAND_GUIDELINES.md files;
- (d) **"Configuration Templates"** — sample configurations, environment files, and deployment schemas.

Unless explicitly stated otherwise, Documentation, Media, and Configuration Templates are provided under this license for reference and non-infringing use. Brand Assets are EXCLUDED from this license and are subject to separate brand guidelines.

1.3 **"Moonlight Games", "MG", "MGFeng",** and **"Feng"** are the original authors and copyright holders of Morget. These terms are used interchangeably in this license.

1.4 **"You"** (or "Your") means any individual or legal entity exercising permissions granted by this license.

1.5 **"Contribution"** means any work of authorship, including modifications or additions, that is intentionally submitted to the copyright holders for inclusion in Morget.

1.6 **"Derivative Work"** means any work based on Morget Software, but shall not include works that merely link to, call, or interface with Morget without incorporating its source code.

1.7 **"Distribute"** means to make available to the public copies of Morget or Derivative Works thereof, in any medium, with or without modifications.

1.8 **"Official Distribution"** means any version of Morget that is explicitly designated as "Official" and distributed directly by Moonlight Games (MG). Only the copyright holders may designate a release as an "Official Morget Distribution."

