### Section 2: Grant of Copyright License (Software)

Subject to the terms of this license, each copyright holder hereby grants to You a perpetual, worldwide, non-exclusive, no-charge, royalty-free, irrevocable copyright license to:

(a) Reproduce, prepare Derivative Works of, publicly display, and Distribute Morget Software;
(b) Use Morget Software in any manner, for any purpose, commercial or non-commercial, including integration into proprietary, closed-source software, SaaS platforms, mobile apps, or embedded systems;
(c) Create and distribute Derivative Works that are proprietary or closed-source, without any obligation to disclose your own source code.

This grant explicitly excludes the official logos, icons, mascots, and brand identity assets of Moonlight Games (MG), which are covered under Section 5 (Trademark Restrictions) and require separate written permission for commercial visual use.

