### Section 3: Grant of Patent License

3.1 **Patent Grant** — Subject to the terms of this license, each contributor hereby grants You a perpetual, worldwide, non-exclusive, no-charge, royalty-free, irrevocable (except as stated in Section 3.3) patent license to make, use, sell, and transfer Morget, where such license applies only to patent claims licensable by such contributor that are necessarily infringed by their Contribution(s).

3.2 **Patent Retaliation** — If You institute patent litigation against any entity alleging that Morget constitutes direct or contributory patent infringement, any patent licenses granted to You under this license shall terminate as of the date such litigation is filed.

3.3 **Patent Non-Assertion** — By using, modifying, or distributing Morget, You agree that You will not initiate or participate in any patent infringement claim against Moonlight Games, MG, MGFeng, Feng, or any other contributor to Morget.

3.4 **Termination of Patent Rights** — If You violate Section 3.3, all patent licenses granted to You under this license are automatically terminated.

