8.1 **No Obligation to Disclose Source Code** — This license is PERMISSIVE and NON-COPYLEFT. You are NOT required to disclose the source code of any modifications, Derivative Works, or integrated software. Unlike the AGPL, this license imposes no network-use source-disclosure obligations.

8.2 **Accepting Warranty or Additional Liability** — You may offer support, warranty, or indemnity for Morget, but only on Your own behalf, and You agree to hold Moonlight Games (MG) harmless from any claims arising from such offers.

8.3 **Severability** — If any provision is invalid under applicable law, it shall be modified to the minimum extent necessary, or severed, leaving the remainder in force.

8.4 **Governing Law** — This license shall be governed by the laws of Malaysia, without regard to conflict of law principles. Any dispute arising under this license shall be subject to the non-exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Malaysia. (You may also bring claims in Your local courts where mandatory consumer protection laws apply.)

