8.6 **Headings** — Headings are for convenience only and have no legal effect.

8.7 **Machine Learning and AI Training** — This license does not by itself grant or restrict the right to use Morget Software or Morget Assets for training machine learning models, large language models (LLMs), or artificial intelligence systems. Unless otherwise prohibited by applicable copyright law, You may use Morget Software for such purposes, provided that any use must comply with the Attribution requirements in Section 4.3. For commercial AI training involving Morget Brand Assets (as defined in Section 1.2(c)) or reproduction of Documentation (Section 1.2(a)) beyond what is permitted by applicable copyright law, separate written permission from Moonlight Games (MG) may be required.

8.8 **Contributions and Developer Certificate of Origin (DCO)** — By submitting a Contribution to Morget, You agree that:

(a) Your Contribution is Your original work, or You have the right to submit it under the terms of this license;
(b) Your Contribution is automatically licensed under the Morget Open License 1 to all recipients, without any additional restriction or royalty;
(c) You certify that You have followed the Developer Certificate of Origin (DCO) by including a "Signed-off-by" line in Your commit message, or You agree to provide such certification upon request.
(d) To ensure compliance, projects hosted on platforms that support automated DCO verification (e.g., GitHub) are encouraged to enable such checks as part of their contribution workflow.
(e) Failure to comply with this Section 8.8 may result in the exclusion of Your Contribution from the Official Distribution.

8.9 **Official Distribution** — Only Moonlight Games (MG) may designate a release of Morget as an "Official Distribution." Forked or modified versions must clearly state they are unofficial derivatives and must not use the official Morget logo or branding without explicit permission.

8.10 **Brand Assets Exclusion** — The official logos, icons, mascots, and visual brand identity assets of Moonlight Games (MG) are NOT licensed under the permissive terms of Section 2. Use of these assets for commercial purposes requires a separate written trademark license from the copyright holders. Detailed usage rules are defined in TRADEMARK.md and BRAND_GUIDELINES.md.

