## How to Apply This License

At the top of each source code file:

```c
/*
 * Morget - [Brief Description]
 * Copyright (C) 2026 Moonlight Games (MG)
 *
 * Licensed under the Morget Open License 1.
 * SPDX-License-Identifier: LicenseRef-MOL-1
 */
```

For the project README or main documentation page:

> This project is based on Morget.
> Copyright (C) 2026 Moonlight Games (MG) / MGFeng / Feng.
> Licensed under the Morget Open License 1.

**SPDX Identifier:** `LicenseRef-MOL-1`

